creator: Coffee Inn
descriptionHtml:
Pay for your coffee with your smartphone. Just add a credit card to our app and:

- pay for coffee with your smartphone;
- get 10% cashback from any coffee purchases;
- track your cashback balance in your phone;
- treat your friend to a cup of coffee via smartphone;
- quickly locate nearest Caffeine café;
- find out latest Caffeine and city news.

Don’t have our coffee card yet? No problem, just add a credit card to the app and we’ll generate one for you automatically, free of charge.
descriptionShort: Caffeine LT loyalty card in your smartphone

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Fixed dark mode issues.
- Fixed bad translations.
